headline: Citigroup Maintains Neutral on AvalonBay Communities, Lowers Price Target to $198
summary: Citigroup  analyst Nick Joseph   maintains AvalonBay Communities (NYSE:AVB) with a Neutral and lowers the price target from $212 to $198.
